functionCall.name: sql_query
functionCall.arguments: {"query":"SELECT b.bank_name AS 'Bank Name', b.bank_account_number AS 'Account Number', b.bank_account_type AS 'Account Type', ie.inc_exp_name AS 'Transaction Name', ie.inc_exp_amount AS 'Amount', ie.inc_exp_type AS 'Type', ie.inc_exp_date AS 'Transaction Date', iec.inc_exp_cat_name AS 'Category Name' FROM banks b JOIN income_expense ie ON b.bank_id = ie.inc_exp_bank JOIN income_expense_category iec ON ie.inc_exp_category = iec.inc_exp_cat_id WHERE MONTH(ie.inc_exp_date) = MONTH(CURDATE()) AND YEAR(ie.inc_exp_date) = YEAR(CURDATE()) AND b.bank_appId = 10001 LIMIT 1000","params":[]}
